    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "df['LogPassengers']= np.log(df['Passengers'])"
      ],
      "metadata": {

      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "Ntest = 12\n",
        "train = df.iloc[:-Ntest]\n",
        "test = df.iloc[-Ntest:]"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "vIP_tBp-ahoh"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# Boolean series to index rows\n",
        "\n",
        "train_idx = df.index <= train.index[-1]\n",
        "test_idx = df.index > train.index[-1]"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "bkG7iomUasnh"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "df['DiffLogPassengers'] = df['LogPassengers'].diff()"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "Su0QP2BybUwS"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# Make supervised dataset\n",
        "\n",
        "series = df['DiffLogPassengers'].dropna().to_numpy()\n",
        "\n",
        "T = 10\n",
        "X = []\n",
        "Y = []\n",
        "for t in range(len(series) - T):\n",
        "  x = series[t:t+T]\n",
        "  X.append(x)\n",
        "  y = series[t+T]\n",
        "  Y.append(y)\n",
        "\n",
        "X = np.array(X).reshape(-1, T, 1)\n",
        "Y = np.array(Y)\n",
        "print(\"X.shape\", X.shape, \"Y.shape\", Y.shape)"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "1FGxj7NgbiIl",
        "outputId": "9a90d43a-9598-47b1-cdbf-ad65d917f2d9"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "X.shape (133, 10, 1) Y.shape (133,)\n"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "Xtrain, Ytrain = X[:-Ntest], Y[:-Ntest]\n",
        "Xtest, Ytest = X[-Ntest:], Y[-Ntest:]"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "Sb3Sg4Z4dF61"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "## CNN"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "GNnqH7kQdkIw"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# CNN\n",
        "\n",
        "i = Input(shape = (T, 1))\n",
        "x = Conv1D(16, 3, activation = 'relu')(i)\n",
        "x = MaxPooling1D(2)(x)\n",
        "x = Conv1D(32, 3, activation = 'relu')(x)\n",
        "x = GlobalMaxPooling1D()(x)\n",
        "x = Dense(1)(x)\n",
        "model = Model(i, x)"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "FJwcJxNcdgJx"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },

        "## Multistep"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "MpMnnp4polww"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# Multi-step forecast \n",
        "\n",
        "multistep_predictions = []\n",
        "\n",
        "# First test input\n",
        "\n",
        "last_x = Xtest[0]\n",
        "\n",
        "while len(multistep_predictions) < Ntest:\n",
        "  # last_x array reshaped because sklearn only accepts 2D input\n",
        "  p = model(last_x.reshape(1, -1))[0]\n",
        "\n",
        "  # Update predictions list\n",
        "  multistep_predictions.append(p)\n",
        "\n",
        "  # Make the new input\n",
        "  last_x = np.roll(last_x, -1)\n",
        "  last_x[-1] = p"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "bnbVPKM_nxDX"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# Save multi-step forecast to the dataframe\n",
        "\n",
        "df.loc[test_idx, 'multistep'] = last_train + np.cumsum(multistep_predictions)"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "ONsVgb8Moruv"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {

    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "## Multi output"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "H4_jkjfQo1jW"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# Make multi-output supervised dataset\n",
        "\n",
        "Tx = T      # number of timesteps in the input\n",
        "Ty = Ntest  # number of timesteps in the output\n",
        "X = []\n",
        "Y = []\n",
        "\n",
        "for t in range(len(series) - Tx - Ty + 1):\n",
        "  x = series[t:t+Tx]\n",
        "  X.append(x)\n",
        "  y = series[t+Tx:t+Tx+Ty]\n",
        "  Y.append(y)\n",
        "\n",
        "X = np.array(X).reshape(-1, Tx)\n",
        "Y = np.array(Y).reshape(-1, Ty)\n",
        "N = len(X)\n",
        "print(\"X.shape\", X.shape, \"Y.shape\", Y.shape)"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "0wz6SP6fo0yM",
        "outputId": "66fa3658-fd85-4edc-8d0b-0f08392983a0"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "X.shape (122, 10) Y.shape (122, 12)\n"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# Split into train and test\n",
        "\n",
        "Xtrain_m, Ytrain_m = X[:-1], Y[:-1]\n",
        "Xtest_m, Ytest_m = X[-1:], Y[-1:]"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "bCsQnfKXo38K"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# CNN\n",
        "\n",
        "i = Input(shape = (Tx, 1))\n",
        "x = Conv1D(16, 3, activation = 'relu')(i)\n",
        "x = MaxPooling1D(2)(x)\n",
        "x = Conv1D(32, 3, activation = 'relu')(x)\n",
        "x = GlobalMaxPooling1D()(x)\n",
        "x = Dense(Ty)(x)\n",
        "model = Model(i, x)"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "O2cwg1EepGZE"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "model.compile(loss = 'mse', optimizer = 'adam')"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "bdiIFzGnpN3e"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "r = model.fit(Xtrain_m, Ytrain_m, epochs = 200, validation_data = (Xtest_m, Ytest_m))"
